Tree-Suffix
===========

This module provides an interface to the libstree generic suffix tree
library.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    libstree from http://www.icir.org/christian/libstree/
    Test::More

A C compiler is required to build this module.

If libstree is installed in a non-standard location (like your home
directory), be sure to pass in the appropriate flags to direct the compiler to
its location, like so:
    perl Makefile.PL INC=-I/home/user/include LIBS="-L/home/user/lib -lstree"

NOTES

Versions of libstree < .4.2 will exhibit a memory leak.

